If we represent this forwarding table as CIDR entries, this is what it looks like. Since

30
00:02:20,250 --> 00:02:24,740
in this simple example all of the prefixes are in terms of bytes, all of the prefixes

31
00:02:24,740 --> 00:02:28,129
have length 0, 8, 16, or 24 bits.

